South Van Horn has a median age of 42.4, with a married population of 49.3%. The average household has 2.51 people. The unemployment rate is 5.5% and the median household income is $39,883.<ref name=":1" /><ref>{{Cite web|title = Best Places to Live in South Van Horn, Alaska|url = http://www.bestplaces.net/city/alaska/south_van_horn|website = www.bestplaces.net|accessdate = 2015-07-19}}</ref>

